[size=14pt][b][color=#00CED1]WHAT'S NEW IN v2.2.1[/color][/b][/size]

[size=12pt][b]Index Fund Token Support (QNK10, DEFI5)[/b][/size]

We've introduced [b]QNK-INDEX[/b] - the world's first post-quantum index fund tokens on a blockchain! Think of it like owning shares in an S&P 500-style fund, but for quantum-resistant crypto assets.

[list]
[li][b]QNK10[/b] - Market-cap weighted index tracking the top 10 QUG ecosystem tokens[/li]
[li][b]DEFI5[/b] - DeFi-focused index with 5 key decentralized finance assets[/li]
[li]Automatic monthly rebalancing based on market conditions[/li]
[li]Low management fees (0.5%) with transparent NAV calculations[/li]
[/list]

